scenes.description: A top-down view of the Congklak (Mancala) board as the members start their game on the beach.
The members discuss their sides and strategy for the game.
The game of Congklak intensifies as they move shells quickly under special house rules.
Zeta makes a big move, picking up many shells while Kobo and Kaela watch from the sand. Zeta eventually wins.
The game concludes with Zeta's victory, and they transition into the MC section of the live stream.
